==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Noun===
'''prepositional case'''

#{{grammar}}: noun [[case]] serving as object of a [[preposition]]. Prepositions that often govern the prepositional case include "about," "in," "on," and "near." [[Russian]] is a language that uses the prepositional case.

